<p>The economics are stark. Traditional identity verification vendors charge <strong>$1-5 per verification</strong>. OpenBiometrics Cloud starts at <strong>$29/month for 10,000 calls</strong> — that's $0.003 per verification. Self-hosted is effectively free beyond server costs.</p>

